Hibernate Query Language

You can perform CRUD operations
1. Insert
2. Update
3. Delete
4. Select



HQL vs SQL

    HQL                                              SQL
 1. Hibernate                                   Database
 2. Database Independant                        Database dependant
 3. HQL queries are Object queries              SQL queries are Table queries


 Insert

1. YOu cannot add a user input data into the table.
2. You can only move one table data into another.

Query q = s.createQuery(...)

q.executeUpdate();  // DML operations
q.uniqueObject();   // DRL operations
q.list();           // DRL operations

Update:
Since Column update is also possible
PK update also possible

